[----------------------------------------------------------------]
[V] — a vector

/obverse
[V]: a list
	[1] — [L]: length of [V]
	[^] gives us an upper bound
	[2] — [P]: tracking position = 0
	[^] allows us to move along [V]
	[~] — [P] < [L]
		[!] — [V]@[P] at index [P]
		[^] the [!] above means log or print
		[1] — [P] += 1
		[^] advance position for the next iteration
